<#
.SYNOPSIS
    This function import a REG file into the Registry.
.DESCRIPTION
    This function is part of the Universal Deployment Script. It contains functions or variables, that are in other files.
.EXAMPLE
    Start-REGFileDeployment -DeploymentObject $MyObject -Action 'Install'
.INPUTS
    [PSCustomObject]
    [System.String]
.OUTPUTS
    [System.Boolean]
.NOTES
